data.description: Welcome to 22 Elmwood Drive, Monroe – a captivating 4~bedroom, 2 full bath, and 1 partial bath residence with an attached carport and open patio, providing the perfect blend of convenience and outdoor enjoyment. Inside, a cozy fireplace graces the living space, and the well~appointed kitchen is a chef's delight. The master suite boasts a luxurious walk~in closet, while the additional bedrooms offer versatility. With modern amenities and timeless charm, this property is a true gem!!!!
